## Description {#details}

This file defines the WebAssembly-specific support for the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/fastisel">FastISel</a> class.

Some of the target-specific code is generated by tablegen in the file WebAssemblyGenFastISel.inc, which is #included here.
